  "title": "Rich Yeasty Peruvian Lamb Seco De Cordero",
  "description": "A tender and flavorful Peruvian dish made with lamb, chickpea flour, and a blend of Mediterranean spices, resulting in a yeasty and savory seco de cordero.",
